Rails Helper Declarations (DRY)
 - availability of methods 

('a'..'z').to_a.shuffle[0..7].join
  to_a -  to character array
  shuffle - randomize
  shuffle[0..7] - returns first 8 random elements of array
  join - joins results of array into one string


